('97747','33729','5','Duplex apartment on the Paseo Maritimo overlooking the marina of Palma de Mallorca'),
('97748','33730','5','This Dublex apartment is located right on the Paseo Maritimo with great views overlooking the marina of Palma de Mallorca. The cameras monitored and safe residential complex was created 1986th The apartment can be reached with a guest lift or a lift from employees. The ca 290m² constructed area is distributed over 2 floors, which are connected with an internal and external staircase. The top floor (3rd floor) has about  40m² terrace and 183m² living space, which is divided into entrance hall, living-dining room, 3 bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite, a white high-quality fitted kitchen, a laundry room and a storage room. The lower floor with about 107m² can be used as a spa. A Jacuzzi, a Finnish sauna, a shower and a toilet are available. Furthermore, it has an office room, a wine cabinet and an over 100m² large terrace. Features include a gas central heating with wall radiators, air conditioning, video door opener and marble flooring. Outside, it has a community pool with sun terraces. 1 underground parking space is included in the sale price'),
